<br />
USAToday actually has a bit more information about the case, including former court cases on the subject - <a href="http://www.usatoday.com/news/washington/2004-09-02-media-sources_x.htm" target="_blank">http://www.usatoday.com/news/washin...a-sources_x.htm</a></div>
